<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><em>同埋左手由第1行去let's say 第5行點樣可以件事快D</em></span><br />\n如果你講緊手唔夠大/手指唔夠長快速轉手指位的話(例如食指按1st fret, 尾指同時/下一個音按5th fret<br />\n1, 唔彈某個音降低難度(chord的話)<br />\n2. 換個細琴<br />\n<br />\n如果係講緊食指由1st fret 去下一個音5th fret[/i]<br />\n1. 滑音(手指轉位其間唔鬆手, 同首歌配合得好可以好有style, 不過界手指唔可以用太多)<br />\n2.轉手指位之前稍微淢速+降低音量掩飾轉手指嘅空檔,不過一首歌唔可以用太多唔係個節奏會受到好大影響"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T10:13:51.000Z","msg":"巴打好勁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f1a5f9dc782e30eaefb83aa811ed804030468c1","tid":1975434,"uid":30662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f4fca20775fe1e47d42c2f56f4f32d69f3aa774","tid":1975434,"uid":126492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T05:25:41.000Z","msg":"啱啱開始學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n手指頭成日揩到其他線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔通手指頭真係太多肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T10:18:32.000Z","msg":"留意下係咪用指尖? 同埋剪指甲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf3ff30be6edd815868fc3fe2c3516cdc995d6e7","tid":1975434,"uid":30662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T10:20:14.000Z","msg":"唔好意思都有d巴打搵我我都係諗住人少少一齊hea玩下, 開group又好似好難manage咁因為咁多人唔知可以點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能係度留自己tg名會人搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33007ff30d6377e5b694ce543262b0028a251a60","tid":1975434,"uid":126492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f1a5f9dc782e30eaefb83aa811ed804030468c1","tid":1975434,"uid":30662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f4fca20775fe1e47d42c2f56f4f32d69f3aa774","tid":1975434,"uid":126492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T05:25:41.000Z","msg":"